        <updateDate>2009-04-02T19:48:36Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Local Officials Tax Relief Act of 2009 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code and title II (Old Age, Survivors and Disability Insurance) of the Social Security Act to exempt from social security taxes certain remuneration paid on or after January 1, 2010, to elected or appointed members of any general governing board, commission, or committee of any political subdivision of a state. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
